<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-top: 4px solid #df1f47;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #df1f47;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .verification-code {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #df1f47, #c0183d);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(223, 31, 71, 0.3);
        }
        .code {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .message {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #df1f47;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .warning-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .company-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #df1f47;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .security-tips {
            background-color: #e8f4fd;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .security-tips h3 {
            color: #0c5460;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .security-tips ul {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .security-tips li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #0c5460;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üîê KNM System</div>
            <h1 class="title">Password Reset Request</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="message">
            <p>Hello <strong><%= user.fname %> <%= user.lname %></strong>,</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset your password. Use the verification code below to proceed with resetting your password:</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="verification-code">
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px;">Your Password Reset Code</p>
            <div class="code"><%= verificationCode %></div>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9;">Enter this code in the app to reset your password</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="warning">
            <div class="warning-icon">‚ö†Ô∏è</div>
            <p><strong>This code will expire in 10 minutes</strong><br>
            Please enter this code in the app to continue with password reset.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="security-tips">
            <h3>üõ°Ô∏è Security Tips</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Never share this verification code with anyone</li>
                <li>Our team will never ask for your verification code</li>
                <li>If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email</li>
                <li>If suspicious activity continues, contact our support team immediately</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p class="message">
            If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email and your password will remain unchanged.
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p class="company-name">KNM System</p>
        <p>This is an automated security message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> KNM. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>